metadata.name: Gravity
metadata.description:
I present # 1 of the GRAVITY DREAMS collection.  Things are distorted, indicative of current events.  She finds herself exhausted, not wanting anyone to see how she feels.  She desires what we all want- peace, rests.

Created by VREG May, 2022

The collector will get the original PNG file in 6000x8000 pixel, 300dpi.
